You are here:
Nonprofit Cloud

Easily store seasonal addresses. Better target your donors by using RFM scores. Quickly add new recurring donations in the gift entry flow. Quickly create individual or batch gift acknowledgments. Remove program participants from all upcoming sessions. Use program cohorts to group participants and make sure that no one slips through the cracks.

Fundraising
Nonprofit Cloud for Fundraising provides new and easy ways to acknowledge donors, enter new recurring donations, store seasonal addresses of constituents, and evaluate donors by using RFM scoring.
Program Management
Group program participants by cohort. Save time with the new Program Management Home Page. Quickly remove one or more participants from all upcoming benefit sessions.

Nonprofit Cloud for Case Management
Caseworkers can use a single guided flow to capture meeting notes; record attendees, date and time, and other details; add tags and upload documents.
Nonprofit Cloud for Grantmaking
Create robust grant applications so that grant seekers can save progress and quickly see sections left to be completed. Track and measure the impact of your grants with Outcome Management.

Action Launcher

Employees can quickly resolve program participants and donor requests by launching Aura components.

Actionable List Members

List creators can add or remove columns in Actionable List Members.

Business Rules Engine

Incorporate new logic into expression set versions efficiently.
Data Processing Engine

Upload large amounts of data into your definition with CSV files.
Intelligent Document Reader

Get Intelligent Document Reader to easily extract unstructured content and tables from documents.
Timeline

Configure a data graph in Timeline to show engagement events from data model objects (DMOs).
